###Block Artificer Subclass																																
Racial Trait ~ Reanimated Companion	CATEGORY:Internal																						ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Reanimated Companion ~ Resistancies|Reanimated Companion ~ Immunities|Reanimated Companion ~ Languages|Reanimated Companion ~ Death Burst|Reanimated Companion ~ Lightning Absorption|Reanimated Companion ~ Dreadful Swipe			BONUS:VAR|BlindsightRange|60|TYPE=Base						SOURCEPAGE:UA

Resistancies	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.ReanimatedCompanionRacialTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Resistance to Necrotic, Poison.	KEY:Reanimated Companion ~ Resistancies																											SOURCEPAGE:UA
Immunities	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.ReanimatedCompanionRacialTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Immunity to Lightning, Charmed, Exhaustion, Poisoned.	KEY:Reanimated Companion ~ Immunities																											SOURCEPAGE:UA
Languages	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.ReanimatedCompanionRacialTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Understands the languages you know	KEY:Reanimated Companion ~ Languages																											SOURCEPAGE:UA
Death Burst	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.ReanimatedCompanionRacialTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The companion explodes when it dies. Dexterity Saving Throw: DC equals your spell save DC, each creature in a 10-foot Emanation originating from the companion. Failure: 2d6 Necrotic damage.	KEY:Reanimated Companion ~ Death Burst																											SOURCEPAGE:UA
Lightning Absorption	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.ReanimatedCompanionRacialTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Whenever the companion is subjected to Lightning damage, it regains a number of Hit Points equal to the Lightning damage dealt.	KEY:Reanimated Companion ~ Lightning Absorption																											SOURCEPAGE:UA
Dreadful Swipe	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.ReanimatedCompanionRacialTrait.SpecialAttack	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Melee Attack Roll: Bonus equals your spell attack modifier, reach 5 ft. Hit: 1d4 + 2 plus your Intelligence modifier Necrotic damage, and the target can’t take Opportunity Attacks until the start of its next turn.	KEY:Reanimated Companion ~ Dreadful Swipe	NATURALATTACK:Dreadful Swipe,Natural.Weapon.Melee.Necrotic,*1,1d4																										SOURCEPAGE:UA
Arcane Conduit	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.ReanimatedCompanionRacialTrait.SpecialAttack	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Once per turn, when master cast an Artificer spell from the Evocation or Necromancy schools and deal damage while you are within 120 feet of your master, master can add your Intelligence modifier to one damage roll of that spell.	KEY:Reanimated Companion ~ Arcane Conduit																											SOURCEPAGE:UA
Ferocity	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.ReanimatedCompanionRacialTrait.SpecialAttack	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When commanded to take the Dreadful Swipe action, you can use it twice.	KEY:Reanimated Companion ~ Ferocity						BONUS:COMBAT|ATTACKS|1																			SOURCEPAGE:UA
Bloated	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.ReanimatedCompanionRacialTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When commanded to take the Dreadful Swipe action, you can use it twice.	KEY:Reanimated Companion ~ Bloated						BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Reanimator Companion Size|1																			SOURCEPAGE:UA
Medium	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.ReanimatedCompanionRacialTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Size Medium.	KEY:Reanimated Companion ~ Bloated ~ Medium						BONUS:SIZEMOD|NUMBER|1																			SOURCEPAGE:UA
Large	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.ReanimatedCompanionRacialTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Size Medium.	KEY:Reanimated Companion ~ Bloated ~ Large						BONUS:SIZEMOD|NUMBER|2																			SOURCEPAGE:UA
Gaunt	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.ReanimatedCompanionRacialTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The companion's Speed increases to 45 feet, and it gains a Climb Speed equal to its Speed. It can climb difficult surfaces, including along ceilings, without needing to make an ability check. In addition, whenever a creature of your choice starts its turn within a 10-foot Emanation originating from your companion, the creature must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw against your spell save DC or have the Frightened condition until the start of its next turn.	KEY:Reanimated Companion ~ Gaunt						BONUS:VAR|RaceBase_Walk|15																			SOURCEPAGE:UA
Moist	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.ReanimatedCompanionRacialTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The companion gains a Swim Speed equal to its Speed. In addition, whenever the companion is hit by an attack roll from a creature within 10 feet of it, the attacker takes Acid damage equal to your Intelligence modifier.	KEY:Reanimated Companion ~ Moist						BONUS:VAR|RaceBase_Swim|30																			SOURCEPAGE:UA
Improved Companion	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.ReanimatedCompanionRacialTrait.SpecialAttack	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The damage of your Reanimated Companion’s Death Burst increases to 4d6. Necrotic damage dealt by your companion ignores Resistance.	KEY:Reanimated Companion ~ Improved Companion																									SOURCEPAGE:UA

